|| IOC (Inversion Of Control ||
-> Spring boot me hame object creat kane ki jarrurat nhai hoti kyu ki spring boot hamare
liye object create kardeta hai isko ham bol hai IOC (Inversion Of Control).
-> Spring me IOC container hota hai jisme hamare project ke classes padi hui hoti hai
or jab bhi hame class ki jarurat padti hai to ham IOC jo container hai spring me usse ham
maang lenge or hame uss particular class ki object bana ni ki jarrurat nhai padti.
-> IOC container ko achive karte hai Application Context ki madat se
*** IMP ***

-> IOC container sari classes ko apne andar nhai rhakega wo scan karega apne packages +
classes and sirf un classes ko rhakega jiske uppar @Component lhika hojise ham annotation
 khete hai .

@Component = jiske uppa rbhi ye lhika ho wo class registerd hojati hai as spring bean
BEAN ka matlab object hota hai bas. @Component se class bean ban jati hai ioc container me
bean = object . or jab bhi koi class bean ban jati hai to wo automatically ioc containcer
me chali jati hai .

